cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on improving depth perception using a fusion of LiDAR and stereo camera data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method is also applicable to robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) fields.
